title: Privacy And Legislative Concerns Are No Reasons To Shy Away From Facebook's Undervalued Stock
text: Legislative concerns may be a challenge for FB because they have become too big to ignore external stakeholder interests. Furthermore, there are privacy-related headwinds with AAPL's new App Store regulations.

title: If Mark Zuckerberg is Facebook's brain, Chris Cox is its heart, employees say
text: After abruptly leaving in March 2019, Chris Cox returned as Facebook's product chief in summer of 2020 -- and many employees are relieved.
